high_descs: Manage to take a side step to your left
Pick up the cell phone off of the table
Turn around and walk to the sofa
Put the cell phone down on the sofa cushion to the left of the box
Turn left twice so that you end up facing a small chest of drawers with a statue on it
Pick up the cell phone off of the chest of drawers
Turn around and head right so you are facing the sofa again
Put the cell phone down on the sofa cushion to the right of the box
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones on the sofa

high_descs: Turn and go to the dresser
Pick up the cell phone on the dresser
Turn and go to the sofa.
Put the cell phone on the sofa.
Turn around and go to the small table by the wall.
Pick up the cell phone on the small table.
Turn around and go to the sofa.
Put the cell phone on the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Put two cells phones on the sofa.

high_descs: Go to the console table and face the far left end of it.
Pick up the white phone from under the television.
Turn around and bring the phone with you over to the black sofa.
Put the phone down on the left seat cushion.
Turn left and cross the room to go to the black table with the golden statue on it.
Pick up the white phone sitting to the right of the statue.
Bring the phone with you back to the black sofa.
Put the phone down on the right seat cushion.
anns.task_desc: Move the phones to the sofa.
